/wiki/Aldona_Grigali\u016bnien\u0117: Aldona Grigaliūnienė is a Paralympian athlete from Lithuania competing mainly in category F37-38 shot putt events.
/wiki/Athletics_at_the_1996_Summer_Paral: Athletics at the 1996 Summer Paralympics consisted of 210 events, 155 for men and 55 for women.
/wiki/K\u0119stutis_Bartk\u0117nas: Kęstutis Bartkėnas is a paralympic athlete from Lithuania competing mainly in category T11 distance running events.
/wiki/Rolandas_Urbonas: Rolandas Urbonas is a paralympic athlete from Lithuania competing mainly in category F12 shot and discus events.
/wiki/Judo_at_the_1996_Summer_Paralympic: Judo at the 1996 Summer Paralympics consisted of seven men's events.
/wiki/Lithuania_at_the_1996_Summer_Paral: Lithuania competed at the 1996 Summer Paralympics in Atlanta, United States.
